## 4. API Routes for AI Services

### Services Requiring Server-Side API Routes

All 22 service files that import `@google/genai` need API route wrappers. These currently read `process.env.API_KEY` which works in Vite only if the env var is available (it often is not on the client, hence the fallback simulations).

### API Route Design

Create 17 API route files under `app/api/ai/`:

