## 5. Component Migration

### Server vs Client Component Classification

**Server Components (no 'use client'):**
- `app/layout.tsx` - Root layout
- `app/(public)/page.tsx` - Landing page (can stay server component if rewritten, OR make it client if reusing the SPA Home component)
- `app/(auth)/layout.tsx` - Auth layout wrapper

**Client Components ('use client' required):**
- ALL 36 migrated page wrappers in `app/(app)/*/page.tsx`
- `app/(app)/layout.tsx` - App layout (manages UI state)
- All components in `components/` - They use React hooks, state, event handlers
- `lib/app-context.tsx` - AppProvider
- `lib/toast-context.tsx` - ToastProvider
- `i18n/context.tsx` - I18nProvider (already client-compatible)

